Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:12.11,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a way to get the\N last word against Takagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:19.01,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just let her keep\N teasing me like this every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:21.75,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:28.67,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.28,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.63,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ah... morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:35.74,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:37.59,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:41.02,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:43.79,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:19.49,Height Comparison,Title 1,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:18.16,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,"Who's Taller?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.03,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Did she see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:26.23,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Did she see what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:28.49,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:29.92,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:32.03,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to tandem ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:36.46,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,No. We'll get in trouble if someone sees us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.67,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're just embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.41,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.59,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:47.06,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like she saw\N me bump into the utility pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.15,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.48,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You finally changed into\N your winter uniform, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:57.94,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's been cold lately,\N so I thought it was time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.79,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.14,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.16,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.30,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.28,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I think that uniform looked\N a little bigger on you last spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.00,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.00,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.65,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,it feels like the uniform fits just right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:20.06,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... that I'm having a growth spurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:27.13,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm growing so much, it kind of sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:29.46,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this is what\N people call a "growth spurt"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:33.15,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't changed much, Takagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.15,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.29,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.17,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,"Haven't changed much"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.83,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:50.54,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not what I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.81,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was talking about height.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.50,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I was talking about height, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.90,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think I meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:04.18,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.39,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:15.05,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Maybe you haven't\N grown that much taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:15.85,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.59,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I did grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.60,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably taller than\N you right now, Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.13,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's see who's taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.75,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Why here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.82,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,We can't tell with our shoes on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.98,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.72,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be quick. Here, turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:54.39,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.39,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda... warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.73,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Takagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:09.44,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you normally stand\N against a wall and put a mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.37,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's more accurate if we\N stand together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.34,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,We're about the same height, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.84,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.66,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you check it out yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.32,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.89,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.56,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,You're not on your tiptoes, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.92,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:42.02,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.19,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,If we face each other, you'll\N know if I'm cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:53.91,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:07.41,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,It-It kinda looks like... I'm taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.54,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I was on my tiptoes earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:13.01,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}were{\i0} cheating! You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.24,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.90,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, you won.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:23.83,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-san, you're acting\N all cool on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:26.48,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,but on the inside, I bet you're really bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:31.65,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and by the way, I'm not bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:32.45,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.89,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when you grow bigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.41,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,you run into utility poles and stuff,\Nand that seems painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.84,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.47,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.61,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.32,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.14,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.93,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.45,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,You're so sensitive\Nto the cold, Yukari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.58,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.01,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Mina, your hand is so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:28.42,Intolerance to Cold,Title 2,0000,0000,0000,,I Hate the Cold
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:27.01,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,"I Hate the Cold"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.88,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.81,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that again, I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.65,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.31,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.95,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Why are your hands so cold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.52,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.23,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,People who have cold hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:52.07,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,have warm hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:56.46,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think a person with a warm\N heart would do what you just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:59.78,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't hold a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.61,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you do it again, I'll be really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.06,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,You're already mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:06.76,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:10.01,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,So cold! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.41,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Sanae-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:14.74,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,"My heart is so warm" attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.48,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Yukari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.18,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:21.77,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,That's for what you guys did earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:26.23,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.59,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari-chan, your hand is warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.40,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,You must have a cold heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.88,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.14,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me, you cold-hearted person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.74,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,"My heart is so cold" attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.35,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.17,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:46.88,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:52.24,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You can get back at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.10,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.56,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:09.52,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.55,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop! It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.65,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,A person with cold hands has a warm heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:19.23,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.12,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-chan and Nishikata-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.73,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,They came to school together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.28,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,They're so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:32.46,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they {\i1}are{\i0} going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.47,Invitation,Title 3,0000,0000,0000,,Invitation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.10,Main,Takao&Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,"Invitation."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:43.86,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nishikata-kun and\N Takagi-chan are going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.31,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:49.80,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You're not interested?\NThey seem really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:52.02,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari, are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:56.53,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh... It's not that I'm jealous, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:10:04.33,Wipe,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe your hands with a\N towel after washing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:01.73,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Mina, Yukari says she wants\Na boy to flirt with!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.49,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.64,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Mina, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.79,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Mina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:11.45,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Sanae-chan, don't talk to me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:14.13,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to pee, but now I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:15.32,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.81,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You're too much, Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:20.81,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch it. It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.48,Main,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'll watch it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.59,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.31,Year 1 Class 2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Year 1 Class 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.77,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I just came up with the ultimate plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.00,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ultimate, fail-proof plan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.87,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,to tease Takagi-san\N on our way home from school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.55,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you smirking about, Nishikata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.41,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Something pervy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:49.25,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.86,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.19,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What I meant was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:53.89,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.63,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Takagi-san. Just wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.27,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Nishikata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.10,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,do you want to\Nwalk home together today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.29,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:12.83,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Did she realize I'm up to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.25,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.28,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you repeat yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.76,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,No reason, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:27.66,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You might change your mind after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.71,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,so you can give me a definite answer then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:32.56,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:40.34,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.88,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she isn't onto me, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.70,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:49.62,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,We're playing "Super-Pro" at my\N house today. You wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.86,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:56.26,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it your girlfriend again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.20,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,"Girlfriend"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.40,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,It's Takagi-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.10,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.40,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,We're not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:06.67,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-chan and Nishikata-kun\N are not going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.83,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,We asked her in the restroom earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.15,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.01,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.84,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I wanna pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.79,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Restroom, restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:21.63,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was she doing in the restroom earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.01,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, Nishikata,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:30.22,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,if you're not going out with Takagi-san,\N why are you walking home with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.68,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:35.83,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that because you two are going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.63,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:40.05,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.32,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.00,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't next period in the science room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.33,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.16,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:13:01.28,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think... Takagi-san just wants to tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which character are you going to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.64,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiromitsu, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:09.02,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,We're going straight home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:09.88,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:13.76,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,I want a Ponkan Popsicle!\N I want a Ponkan Popsicle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.91,Main,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You want a popsicle in this\N freezing weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.47,Main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Eating a popsicle in the kotatsu is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:19.36,Main,Sanae,0000,0000,0000,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:24.07,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,She wants an answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:27.41,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,so that means she wants me to ask her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:31.38,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.43,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been the one to ask her\Nto walk home with me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:36.73,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.00,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it, Takagi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:43.48,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good! If Takagi-san asks,\N all I have to say is yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:48.93,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone asked me today if\N I was going out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:49.73,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:55.35,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,And they think I'm the one\N who's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:14:00.39,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's because I'm always the one\N asking you to walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:05.63,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Takagi-san! So\N this was what you were after!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.60,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,You created a situation\N where I have to ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:13.31,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,just so you can enjoy watching me squirm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:15.88,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.99,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Try to sound calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.83,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "Oh, really?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:24.80,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, r-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.07,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:30.99,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, about your request from this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:35.56,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't have any plans, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.14,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:42.31,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.77,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:49.70,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,If I get through this, I can tease Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:52.66,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.59,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,walk home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.90,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.00,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.90,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.74,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.73,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're scheming something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.74,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,She knows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:29.86,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,If she knows, should I not execute my plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.12,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,But I came up with such a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:37.50,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even thought of how to carry\N out the plan to begin with, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.26,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Want to buy juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:48.21,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm parched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.41,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, most of them are sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.47,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted something cold, but all they have is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.52,Black Signs,Can,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious Sweet Red Bean Soup
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.52,Hot,Red label,0000,0000,0000,,Hot
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.52,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,sweet red bean soup
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.14,Cold,Blue lebel,0000,0000,0000,,Cold
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.14,Wormwood Juice,Can,0000,0000,0000,,Wormwood Juice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.82,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,and some weird stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:04.24,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:08.07,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I'll regret it\N no matter what I choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.59,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll regret it no matter what I choose"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.96,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Should we find another vending machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.29,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.85,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty, so I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.97,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... Gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.18,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't tell from\Nthe way it looked?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.02,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I completely regret getting this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:42.28,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,But now I can carry out my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.77,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:49.35,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say one juice is really\N tasty but gives you a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.69,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,and the other juice is just plain disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.25,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:02.00,Two Choice,Title 4,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Choice Question
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.71,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,"Two-Choice Question."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:05.45,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,A very tasty juice that gives you a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.96,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,or a juice that's plain disgusting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.42,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Takagi-san?\N You can't choose, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:16.51,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Feel the unease, and let me see that\N uneased face of yours, Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.14,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:25.56,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,If I drink the tasty juice and get\N a fever, will you come visit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:30.30,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? D-Does that have anything\N to do with your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.52,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Significantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:33.99,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't come and see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:42.31,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you had a fever, I guess I'd go visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.50,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then I choose the tasty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.07,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:48.73,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.63,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,This is weird. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:56.59,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-san isn't troubled at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:01.73,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,The only one troubled here... is me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:05.57,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,The "two-choice question" plan has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.77,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! It's too early to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.81,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Next question, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.32,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:16.15,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,No allowance for life, or no more teasing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.07,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,No allowance for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.07,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:24.38,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saving up my New Year's money,\N so I'd be fine for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:26.60,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Once I enter high school,\N I'll just start a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:30.08,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd rather keep teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:35.05,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated her!\N I have to ask a better question!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.34,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.14,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.84,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You've been asking weird questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.66,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,but are you trying to give me a hard time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.94,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.94,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you a question this time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.07,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather me disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.84,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,or continue to be teased by me forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:57.91,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.90,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,"Disappear"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.82,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:06.24,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:10.08,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be teased,\Nbut for her to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.54,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.75,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'd choose to be teased.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:20.85,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,So you do like to be teased, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:23.96,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:28.76,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,But... you disappearing\N is not really what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.87,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you want to be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.43,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.61,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:42.07,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Takagi-san!\N Is it {\i0}that{\i1} fun to see me squirm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:45.41,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I have to come up\Nwith a really good question!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.43,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.04,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,We're still doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.95,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a zero on all your tests for life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.37,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,or kissing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:54.63,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.88,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.38,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,K-Ki—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:01.75,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:05.79,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a zero, even if I study?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.76,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. A zero no matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:10.90,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:15.87,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,That'll mean I'll never get any more\Nallowance, and I can't even enter high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:20.40,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,But if I choose the kiss,\N she'll definitely make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:22.50,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't choose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:26.85,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... The more I struggle to choose,\Nthe happier she looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.54,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I have to choose quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:32.63,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a zero on the tests is too much! But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:34.46,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:39.21,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, the one that doesn't\N get me a zero on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:41.04,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Which one would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.92,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The one with the kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.68,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.86,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.10,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.73,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little taller than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:19.11,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nishikata?\N I was just seeing who's taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.63,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,She's made fun of me so many times today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.62,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,But I have this all figured out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:43.38,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,On option has to be\Nsomething she'd never choose,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:46.14,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,and the other is simply to make fun of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.40,Italics,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I'll definitely win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.22,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-san, the next questio—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:51.74,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:52.87,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:56.37,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Go around the campus doing\N a handstand, or the two of us—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:59.57,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! I can't do a handstand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:02.34,Main,Nishikata,0000,0000,0000,,And, like, when can I ask the questions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.18,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,You have to answer my question first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:04.98,Main,NIshikata,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
